<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f5f5f5; font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#f5f5f5; padding:20px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff; border-radius:8px; overflow:hidden;">
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color:#E8621A; padding:30px; text-align:center;">
              <h1 style="color:#ffffff; margin:0; font-size:28px;">&#127875; Sunshine Pumpkins</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <!-- Body -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:30px;">
              <h2 style="color:#3D2B1F; margin-top:0;">Your Pumpkin Display is Installed!</h2>
              <p style="color:#555; line-height:1.6;">Hi <%= customer.first_name %>,</p>
              <p style="color:#555; line-height:1.6;">Your pumpkin display has been installed and is looking fantastic! We hope you love it as much as we loved creating it.</p>

              <h3 style="color:#3D2B1F;">Care Tips</h3>
              <div style="background-color:#FFF3E0; border-left:4px solid #E8621A; padding:15px; margin:20px 0; border-radius:4px;">
                <ul style="color:#555; line-height:1.8; margin:0;">
                  <li>Keep pumpkins out of direct afternoon sun when possible</li>
                  <li>Mist with water every few days to keep them fresh</li>
                  <li>Avoid placing near heat sources</li>
                  <li>If a pumpkin starts to soften, contact us for a replacement</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <h3 style="color:#3D2B1F;">Want to Add More?</h3>
              <p style="color:#555; line-height:1.6;">Love your display? Consider adding some extras to make it even more special:</p>
              <ul style="color:#555; line-height:1.8;">
                <li>Additional pumpkins for your walkway</li>
                <li>Gourd and mum accents</li>
                <li>Hay bale arrangements</li>
                <li>Seasonal lighting</li>
              </ul>
              <p style="color:#555; line-height:1.6;">Just reply to this email and we'll get you set up!</p>

              <p style="color:#E8621A; font-weight:bold;">The Sunshine Pumpkins Team</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color:#3D2B1F; padding:20px; text-align:center;">
              <p style="color:#999; font-size:12px; margin:0;">Sunshine Pumpkins | St. Petersburg, FL</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
